org.sonatype.restsimple.spi
Class ServiceHandlerMapper

java.lang.Object
  org.sonatype.restsimple.spi.ServiceHandlerMapper

public class ServiceHandlerMapper
extends Object

A URI mapper for ServiceHandler. It is recommended to let Guice inject instance of that class. Having multiple instance can cause mapping issue (not found) if the wrong instance of that class get used.
